    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Times's six-week report ''How Race Is Lived in America'' concludes today with a special issue of The Times Magazine that removes the journalistic filter, and through memoir, dialogue and photograph, gets straight to the complex feelings on an issue that continues to be a source of both misunderstanding and enlightenment.</p>
      </block>
